  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Arbitrary Rotation</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Beliebig drehen</phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Rotation arbitraire</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">任意旋转</phrase>
  </title>

  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Layer</primary>
    <secondary>Rotate arbitrary</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de">
    <primary>Ebene</primary>
    <secondary>drehen</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr">
    <primary>Calque</primary>
    <secondary>Rotation</secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Arbitrary Rotation</guimenuitem> command rotates a
    layer by a specified angle. It is an alternate way of accessing the
    <link linkend="gimp-tool-rotate">Rotate tool</link>. See the section
    about that tool for more information.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    Mit diesem Kommando können Sie eine Ebene um einen beliebigen Winkel drehen.
    Hierzu verwendet <application>GIMP</application> das Werkzeug
    <quote>Drehen</quote>, welches im <xref linkend="gimp-tool-rotate" />
    ausführlich beschrieben ist.
  </para>
  <para lang="fr">
    C'est une autre manière d'activer l'outil  
    <link linkend="gimp-tool-rotate">Rotation</link>.
  </para> 


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activating the Command</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Kommandos</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>L</accel>ayer</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransform</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>rbitrary Rotation</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Kommando kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransformation</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>B</accel>eliebig</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          On accède à ces commandes à partir de la barre de menu de l'image 
          par 
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>C</accel>alque</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransformer</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Rotation ar<accel>b</accel>itraire</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          该命令在图像菜单的
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>图层</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>变换</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>自由旋转</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>，它是另外一种执行<link linkend="gimp-tool-rotate">旋转工具</link>的方式。
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem lang="en;de;fr">
        <para lang="en">
          or by using the keyboard shortcut
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap>
            <keycap>R</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Alternativ können Sie das Tastenkürzel
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap>
            <keycap>R</keycap>
          </keycombo>
          verwenden.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          ou en utilisant la combinaison de touches 
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Shift</keycap>
            <keycap>R</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
